@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Open Class Meeting Details

start

:Logged-in user opens Public Weekly Schedule;
:System loads current-week class meetings;
:System displays public meeting rows;
:User selects a class meeting;

if (User is Administrator?) then (yes)
  :Open full ClassMeetingDetailsView;
elseif (User is Teacher assigned to meeting?) then (yes)
  :Open full ClassMeetingDetailsView;
elseif (User is Student in meeting group?) then (yes)
  :Open full ClassMeetingDetailsView;
  :Show details as read-only;
  :Show own attendance status if available;
else (no)
  :Show public schedule information only;
  :Display "Only public schedule information is available for this class meeting.";
  stop
endif

:Display subject, type, group, teacher, email, date, time, mode, status, comment;

if (User is Student?) then (yes)
  :Disable edit and attendance actions;
else (Teacher or Administrator)
  :Show comment and attendance actions according to role;
endif

stop
@enduml
